000983r 2  AA             tax
000984r 2  BD rr rr       lda DisMnemonics,x
000987r 2  DA             phx
000988r 2  20 rr rr       jsr Chrout
00098Br 2  FA             plx
00098Cr 2  BD rr rr       lda DisMnemonics+1,x
00098Fr 2  DA             phx
000990r 2  20 rr rr       jsr Chrout
